Search for a Book by Title

  As a user I want to be able to use the search field so that I can find a book by its title

  Scenario: User searches for a book by title
    Given the user is on the book store website
    When the user enters "Catching fire" into the search field
    And the user submits the search query
    Then the search results page should be displayed
    And the search results should include "Catching fire "

Search for a Book by Author

  As a user I want to be able to use the search field so that I can find a book by its author

  Scenario: User searches for a book by author
    Given the user is on the book store website
    When the user enters "Christina Lauren" into the search field
    And the user submits the search query
    Then the search results page should be displayed
    And the search results should include "Christina Lauren"
